OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1772549423
OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,C'targeted' stabbing in Yorkshire
OL,5,Cvillage
OL,7,FThree people have been arrested after
OL,8,Fa man was stabbed in a Yorkshire
OL,9,Fvillage on Sunday morning.
OL,11,FPolice were called to the junction of
OL,12,FMain Street and Iron Row in Burley in
OL,13,FWharfedale just before 10am.
OL,15,FA man, believed to be in his thirties,
OL,16,Fwas found with a stab wound and taken
OL,17,Fto hospital - he remains in critical
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
