FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1772549423
OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,C'targeted' stabbing in Yorkshire
OL,5,Cvillage
OL,7,FA 30-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of attempted murder, and two
OL,9,Fwomen - both aged 23 - have been
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of conspiracy to
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FAll three remain in custody for
OL,14,Fquestioning.
OL,16,FPolice cordons are still in place
OL,17,Faround the area and police continue to
OL,18,Fappeal for any witnesses to come
OL,19,Fforward.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1772549423
OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,C'targeted' stabbing in Yorkshire
OL,5,Cvillage
OL,7,FDCI Michael Cox of West Yorkshire
OL,8,FPolice, said it was a 'targeted and
OL,9,Fisoaletd' attack.
OL,11,F"Multiple police enquiries are ongoing
OL,12,Ftoday into what has clearly been a
OL,13,Fvery serious assault on a victim in
OL,14,FBurley and Wharfedale.
OL,16,F"We realise this incident will cause
OL,17,Fconcern locally, but I want to assure
OL,18,Fresidents we do think this incident
OL,19,Fwas isolated and targeted, and that we
OL,20,Fhave all necessary resources in the
OL,21,Farea to investigate what took place.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
