OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1772549423
OL,3,CMan in critical condition after
OL,4,C'targeted' stabbing in Yorkshire
OL,5,Cvillage
OL,7,F"Police activity will continue at
OL,8,Flocations throughout the day, and we
OL,9,Fare appealing for witnesses."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
